title: Tom Clancys Rainbow Six Siege Ultra HD Texture Pack-PLAZA
description:
Tom Clancy's: Rainbow Six Siege - Ultra HD Texture Pack
Release Date: 12/2015 Protection: Uplay
Discs: 1 Genre: Action

This is the official Ultra-HD texture pack for update v1.1

1. Extract
2. Run setup.exe and install textures pack
3. Copy crack from PLAZA dir to installdir
4. Play

This pack requires:

Tom.Clancys.Rainbow.Six.Siege-CODEX
Tom.Clancys.Rainbow.Six.Siege.Update.v1.1-CODEX

or:

Tom.Clancys.Rainbow.Six.Siege.MULTi14-PLAZA
Tom.Clancys.Rainbow.Six.Siege.Update.v1.1-CODEX

General Notes:

Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online
If you install games to your systemdrive, it may be necessary
to run this game with admin privileges instead
